                                </msItem>

                                <msItem xml:id="ms_i21">
                                    <locus from="108r"/>
                                    <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2120OntheE">John Chrysostom, on Easter Sunday</title>
                                    <incipit xml:lang="gez">በእንተ፡ ቅድስት፡ ፋሲካ፡ ዘይትንበብ፡ በዓባይ፡ ዕለጥ።</incipit>
                                    <note>On the margin: <foreign xml:lang="gez">በዕለጥ፡ ፋሲካ፡ መንባብ፡</foreign></note>
                                </msItem>

                                <msItem xml:id="ms_i22">
                                    <locus from="111v"/>
                                    <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1265Dersan">(Gregory) Theologus, on Easter Sunday</title>
                                    <incipit xml:lang="gez">ድርሳን፡ ዘቅዱስ፡ ወበፁዕ፡ ቴዎጎሎስ፡ በእንተ፡ ቅድስት፡ ፋሲካ፡</incipit>
                                    <note>On the margin: <foreign xml:lang="gez">በሰኑየ፡ ፋሲካ፡ ም፡ </foreign></note>
                                </msItem>

                                <msItem xml:id="ms_i23">
