                                    <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2140OntheR">John Chrysostom, on Lazarus</title>
                                    <incipit xml:lang="gez">በእንተ፡ አልዓዛር፡ ዘአንሥኦ፡ እግዚእነ፡ እምዉታን፡ እምድኅረ፡ ረቡዕ።</incipit>
