                                    <incipit xml:lang="gez">በእንተ፡ ሳምራዊት፡</incipit>
                                    <note>On the margin: <foreign xml:lang="gez">በኃሙስ፡ ፋሲካ፡ ም፡ </foreign></note>
                                </msItem>

                                <msItem xml:id="ms_i26">
