                                    <note>On the margin: <foreign xml:lang="gez">በዐርብ፡ ፋሲካ፡ ም፡</foreign></note>
                                </msItem>

                                <msItem xml:id="ms_i27">
                                    <locus from="134v"/>
                                    <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT6454Dersan">on the great Spiritual Easter</title>
                                    <incipit xml:lang="gez">ድርሳን፡ ዘደረሰ፡ ርቱዐ፡ ሃይማኖት፡ ... ዘቅድስት፡ ፋሲካ፡ ዓባይ፡ ወመንፈሳዊት።</incipit>
